A presentation of the Tera-10 system, the number 1 supercomputer in Europe (and number 5 in the world according to the TOP500Â® ranking of June 2006), designed and installed by Bull for CEA, France's Atomic Energy Authority. This presentation will cover the different technologies that are at the heart of Tera-10, the overall architecture of the system, as well as the issues that had to be addressed by the implementation team.